{"tid":634992,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】開到飲早荼 Day198 20/4","createTime":"2018-04-19T17:32:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T23:13:43.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2ad52ad37ec8ec1936efbe7426d1f23bfe07581e","tid":634992,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T17:32:02.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=2uC3t%2Br9CkjFZ%2FF5riHAvdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=34fb9b09\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，<br />\n希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=2uC3t%2Br9CkjFZ%2FF5riHAvdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=8f60f1fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a></div>"},{"pid":"c36ff9da83f677ec6a6ce9a6ecb6c8f4db94a096","tid":634992,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T17:32:26.000Z","msg":"已開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb461ccc82e9c200781ccee2f4e6aedf78e1b102","tid":634992,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T17:35:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00bb470741949ad62969d37fd893dca6eacae388","tid":634992,"uid":122942